---
title: Chicken & Pesto Fettuccine Alla Genovese with Garlic Bread & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Presenting a few of our favourite things: juicy chicken, herbaceous basil pesto and golden ropes of fettuccine! All of this deliciousness is tossed through with baby broccoli, lemon and garlic for a bright and indulgent meal.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67e0ea4cf8f6928425d5c033-a749e597-ea39b24a.jpeg
